{"tid":2336134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有黃app上架喇! 屬於香港人嘅家居保養黃app!","createTime":"2020-12-22T11:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:26:57.000Z","uid":110581,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4700846ef4e70e5204a23406e84b33f5719eb5c8","tid":2336134,"uid":110581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"首先祝各位巴絲聖誕快樂!<br />\n相信唔少人都對香港嘅疫情感到無奈, 正苦遲遲唔肯封關, 無啦啦話喉管洩漏又擾流呢啲問題又唔知點check, 管理公司唔理, 到出事嘅時候真係喊出嚟, 香港人都係要靠自己!<br />\n<br />\n小弟本身就做緊測量狗 (識我嘅朋友勿相認) 因為以上嘅問題, 我大約半年前開始膽粗粗由零開始自學寫app, 到最近總算寫到個用得嘅version.<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲嚟講, 個app係一個配對住戶同測量師嘅平台, 住戶有任何家居保養維修問題可以喺個app到出post, 測量師就可以報價接case, 再喺chatroom到同住戶了解下情況, 傾好細節就再約時間上門檢查. 個app主要都係想幫大家處理一啲日常生活遇到嘅問題, 所以唔需要話整個report之類, 係上樓做inspection, 然後解答巴絲client嘅疑難, 避免傳統綑綁式貴價全套service, 當然巴絲都可以指明想要嘅服務然後等測量巴絲報價!<br />\n<br />\n個app免費下載, 唔會向測量師巴絲收佣金, 喺度都做少少宣傳, 邀請各界測量師巴絲註冊, 賺少少外快又幫到同路人!<br />\n<br />\n另外, 整呢個app其中一個原因係希望黃圈可以突破B2C嘅模式. 當然除咗本身想為黃圈出一分力, 我都係想趁後生嘗試創業, 希望我嘅少少創新可以幫到人.<br />\n<br />\n小弟小試牛刀, 歡迎提出任何建議! Update會慢啲... 但我會盡力! 始終本身有正職同埋新手programmer. 多謝大家睇到呢度, 香港人加油.<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以下載支持下! <br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/surver/id1519262130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fsurver%2Fid1519262130&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=40f26e65\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/surver/id1519262130</a> <br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.surver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.surver&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=7d7753ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.surver</a> <br />\n<br />\n睇完都請大家繼續關注12港人, 在囚或流亡嘅手足, 同埋買爆黃店! 聖誕快樂!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q75pkxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq75pkxE.jpg&h=297d4cb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ef9cd60463c290f3c9fe889b98829121913028e","tid":2336134,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4edb45edcc6edc86a44406d7445e7503f1664718","tid":2336134,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b503b068913d05167ba2b8f08a24c3a8bb1c4f1d","tid":2336134,"uid":374427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳下活動：<br />\n<br />\n快d入黎平安夜活動頻道!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2336042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2336042</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67284b71d616d397090daccce8294a419ce13bf1","tid":2336134,"uid":129883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b5b453e72acf71ce770dca868d6980e12d04f493","tid":2336134,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"Support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396efc81d258c8447cef759b6562e875411137c4","tid":2336134,"uid":68464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}